				<h3>WikiFindings</h3>
				<p>A dynamic repository of lay summaries of research articles.</p>
				<h5 class="projectLink">Live now at <a href="https://www.wikifindings.net">wikifindings.net</a></h5>
				<h5 class="projectLink"><a href="https://github.com/remdd/wikifindings">View on GitHub <i class="devicon-github-plain"></i></a></h5>

